Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以學生的安全為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西區確認完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有男生抵抗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 給點教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對方只是高中生別讓他受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 八田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在預料之內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作聯絡 工作聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現藍制服的傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責大門的隊伍加強戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人真的在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正學園島已經封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經舉手可得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面到底是什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在那嘰嘰喳喳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒能阻止赤之王的逃獄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還造成這樣的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你飽受屈辱的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,室長！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說沒能阻止赤之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為此感到責任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點自以為是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過事態真是變得麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
